room_title: Escape room "The Fallout Shelter" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
room_description: After receiving news of an imminent nuclear attack your group heads to the nearest fallout shelter. In your rush to get to safety, you hurry in closing and locking the door behind you... But oops, you didn't activate the emergency life support generator first! You now have one hour to escape before your room runs out of oxygen!
